sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant App
  participant DB as Local DB
  participant Widget as Widget Extension
  participant Notif as Notification Scheduler
  participant ML as ML Generator

  User->>App: Open app
  App->>DB: Load preferences + daily affirmation
  DB-->>App: Data
  App-->>User: Show affirmation card

  User->>App: Favorite
  App->>DB: Save favorite
  App->>Widget: Update widget snapshot (App Group)

  User->>App: Enable reminders
  App->>Notif: Schedule next 7 days
  Notif-->>User: Notifications delivered

  User->>App: Generate background
  App->>ML: Run on-device diffusion
  ML-->>App: Generated image + metadata
  App->>DB: Save theme record
